OL,3,CCritics say plans to fix cladding is
OL,4,C"Totally laughable and unachievable"
OL,6,FAs the government announces that
OL,7,Fdangerous cladding on high-rise
OL,8,Fbuildings to be fixed by 2029 a lease
OL,9,Fholder in Manchester has raised
OL,10,Fconcerns.
OL,12,FThe Remediation Acceleration Plan will
OL,13,Fset out that by the end of 2029, all
OL,14,Fbuildings over 18 metres tall `
OL,15,Fdefined as high-rise ` with unsafe
OL,16,Fcladding that are on a Government
OL,17,Fscheme will have been remediated.
