OL,3,CCritics say plans to fix cladding is
OL,4,C"Totally laughable and unachievable"
OL,6,FRuth Guest has owned her apartment in
OL,7,FManchester for twenty years and is
OL,8,Fdoubtful the target will be reached.
OL,9,FShe said "Like many of the
OL,10,Fleaseholders in the country I was
OL,11,Fstuck in a property that we couldn't
OL,12,Fsell. It was a zero valued property.
OL,13,FWe couldn't get a mortgage for it so
OL,14,Flife became in limbo. We couldn't do
OL,15,Fanything.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
