OL,3,CCritics say plans to fix cladding is
OL,4,C"Totally laughable and unachievable"
OL,6,F"We have had leaseholders who have had
OL,7,Fto put off their wedding plans or
OL,8,Fstarting a family. Their career
OL,9,Fprospects have been put on hold. If
OL,10,Fthey have been able to move they have
OL,11,Fbecome accidental landlords because
OL,12,Fthey cannot sell their property. It is
OL,13,Fjust crazy. It is heartbreaking.
OL,15,F"Ruth is waiting for a 'waking watch'
OL,16,Fbill - a fire safety system where
OL,17,Fsuitably trained staff continually
OL,18,Fpatrol the floors and the external
OL,19,Fperimeter of a building to maintain
OL,20,Fthe safety of occupants.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
