OL,3,CCritics say plans to fix cladding is
OL,4,C"Totally laughable and unachievable"
OL,6,FRuth said "It is crazy. Fortunately
OL,7,Ffor me I am a qualifying lease holder
OL,8,Fbecause I own less that four
OL,9,Fproperties so I have got protection up
OL,10,Fto #1000 per year. For non qualifying
OL,11,Fleaseholders who own four or more
OL,12,Fproperties they are liable for the
OL,13,Fwhole cost. We are sitting here as
OL,14,Finnocent victims.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
