OL,3,CCritics say plans to fix cladding is
OL,4,C"Totally laughable and unachievable"
OL,6,FI just cannot see how a 2029 deadline
OL,7,Fis achievable. Four and a half years
OL,8,Fafter the building safety fund opened
OL,9,Fwe are not really anymore forward. How
OL,10,Fare they going to achieve it in five
OL,11,Fyears? It is totally laughable and
OL,12,Funachievable.
OL,14,F"This is my safe haven or should be my
OL,15,Fsafe haven but every time I open my
OL,16,Fdoor I get a reminder. That 'waking
OL,17,Fwatch' walking around. A constant
OL,18,Freminder of how dangerous this
OL,19,Fbuilding is.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
