OL,6,FRuth management company has said it
OL,7,Fwill get in touch with Granada Reports
OL,8,Fin fifteen days. It adds it is working
OL,9,Fdiligently to remedy the issue.
OL,11,FThe announcement comes more than seven
OL,12,Fyears after the Grenfell Tower fire
OL,13,Fkilled 72 people.
